            "title": "全日收市｜港股收跌335點  內銀捱沽  恒指4 月升988點科指升近半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股收跌335點，晶片股一枝獨秀，內銀股績後捱沽，資源及內需股均受壓，一周計恒生指數累跌202點，但4 月份升988點，升幅接近4%，恒生科技指數本周報跌，4月升近4.8%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數全日收報25776，跌335點或1.28%，今早開市報26008點，跌103點或0.4%，早段見26072，僅跌39點或0.14%，為全日高位，全日最低見25734，跌377點或1.44%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">內地銀行。AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"比亞迪。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/925c8ee6769927f598ce77821ca56a78_Thailand_Auto_Show_67_88.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/925c8ee6769927f598ce77821ca56a78_Thailand_Auto_Show_67_88.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">比亞迪。AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">內地銀行。AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/925c8ee6769927f598ce77821ca56a78_Thailand_Auto_Show_67_88.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">比亞迪。AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數全日報4871，跌38點或0.79%，今早開報4876點，跌33點或0.68%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生國企指數全日報8681，跌123點或1.41%，今早以8757點開市，跌47點或0.54%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交2915.53億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指報25624，跌316點或1.22%，低水153點 ; 科指期貨全日報4876，跌36點或0.73%，高水5點，國指期貨全日報8654，跌114點或1.3%，低水28點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結本周，恒指累跌202點或0.77%，4月累升988點或3.98% ; 科指一周累跌31點或0.63%，4月累升222點或4.77% ; 國指一周跌94點或1.07%，4月升307點或3.66%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股午後升幅再擴大，中芯國際(00981)收升7.75%，報70.9元，貢獻恒指34點，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 華虹半導體(01347)升5.55%，報114.1元，成交入20大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內銀股首季業績公布後捱沽，建設銀行(00939)跌2.34%，報8.78元 ; 工商銀行(01398)跌2.63%，報7.03元 ; 中國銀行(03988)跌2.32%，報5.06元 ; 農業銀行(01288)跌1.46%，報6.08元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">內地銀行。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國人壽(02628)全日升4.45%，報28,62元，首季新業務價值升75.5%勝預期，今早公布季績的友邦(01299)最高見87.15元，升2.58%，收升0.12%，報85.05元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">比亞迪(01211)跌5.36%，報102.5元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 理想汽車(02015)跌2.46%，報67.55元 ; 小鵬(09868)跌2.4%，報61元，中國乘聯會公布，4月26日新能源市場零售量「雙降」。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"比亞迪。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/925c8ee6769927f598ce77821ca56a78_Thailand_Auto_Show_67_88.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/925c8ee6769927f598ce77821ca56a78_Thailand_Auto_Show_67_88.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">比亞迪。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內需股午後跌幅擴大，康師傅(00322)挫4.89%，報12.05元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位; 萬洲(00288)跌4.42%，報9.52元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">資源股跑輸，中國宏橋(01378)報32.68元，跌4.67% ; 洛陽鉬業(03993)跌3.67%，報17.6元 ; 紫金礦業(02899)跌2.14%，報35.68元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科網股拖低大市，阿里巴巴(09988)挫3.52%，報126元，影響恒指70點；騰訊(00700)報467.8元，跌2.38%，拖低恒指46點，兩股成跌市主力。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">長飛光纖(06869)全日瀉13.78%，報199元，跌破200元關，公司公布首季多賺226.4%，至4.95億元人民幣，績後股價大幅回吐。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15944861-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c335%e9%bb%9e-%e5%85%a7%e9%8a%80%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%874-%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%87988%e9%bb%9e%e7%a7%91",
